}, {\"ngram\": \"their first competition\", \"from\": 168, \"to\": 191}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 198, \"to\": 213}, {\"ngram\": \"the inaugural Rockstar Energy Open\", \"from\": 217, \"to\": 251}]}, {\"sentence\": \"True to its name, the event aimed to give up-and-coming skateboarders and pros who do not always make limited invite-only fields in other competitions an opportunity to compete.\", \"from\": 295, \"to\": 472, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its name\", \"from\": 303, \"to\": 311}, {\"ngram\": \"skateboarders\", \"from\": 351, \"to\": 364}, {\"ngram\": \"pros\", \"from\": 369, \"to\": 373}, {\"ngram\": \"limited invite-only fields\", \"from\": 397, \"to\": 423}, {\"ngram\": \"other competitions\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 445}, {\"ngram\": \"an opportunity\", \"from\": 446, \"to\": 460}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For some, it was their first pro-level contest-and they capitalized on the chance, like Lazer Crawford did when he beat out five Paris 2024 Olympians to win the men's street final.\", \"from\": 474, \"to\": 654, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 568, \"end\": 576, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamal_Crawford\", \"score\": 0.9914551286230394, \"rank\": 0.008618515483253056, \"text\": \"Crawford\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamal_Crawford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamal_Crawford\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their first pro-level contest\", \"from\": 491, \"to\": 520}, {\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 545, \"to\": 555}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympians\", \"from\": 614, \"to\": 623}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's street final\", \"from\": 631, \"to\": 653}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Multiple amateurs, like 16-year-old Secret Lynn, who earned a spot in the competition through the event's Video Qualifying Series, made it to the final, earning invaluable exposure and experience.\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 852, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Multiple amateurs\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 673}, {\"ngram\": \"16-year-old Secret Lynn\", \"from\": 680, \"to\": 703}, {\"ngram\": \"a spot\", \"from\": 716, \"to\": 722}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 741}, {\"ngram\": \"the event's Video Qualifying Series\", \"from\": 750, \"to\": 785}, {\"ngram\": \"invaluable exposure\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 836}, {\"ngram\": \"experience\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 851}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think a lot of kids think the best way to do it is to go straight into the Olympic qualifiers, and that's not a bad thing, but it definitely helps having some less strenuous contests, less pressure, and kind of ease into it,\\\" said Tate Carew, who competed on the U.S. men's park team at Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 854, \"to\": 1155, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1088, \"end\": 1092, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tate_Modern\", \"score\": 0.8649399442689276, \"rank\": 0.15605211850804981, \"text\": \"Tate\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q33506\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tate_Modern\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tate_Modern\"}, {\"begin\": 1093, \"end\": 1098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rod_Carew\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.897822566704426e-20, \"text\": \"Carew\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rod_Carew\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rod_Carew\"}, {\"begin\": 1120, \"end\": 1124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.8624384304292815, \"rank\": 0.15459992517345986, \"text\": \"U.S.\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 868}, {\"ngram\": \"kids\", \"from\": 872, \"to\": 876}, {\"ngram\": \"the best way\", \"from\": 883, \"to\": 895}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic qualifiers\", \"from\": 928, \"to\": 950}, {\"ngram\": \"a bad thing\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 978}, {\"ngram\": \"some less strenuous contests\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1039}, {\"ngram\": \"less pressure\", \"from\": 1041, \"to\": 1054}, {\"ngram\": \"kind of ease\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1072}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1149}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For Carew and the dozens of other invited skateboarders coming off the two-year process that is qualifying for and competing in the Olympics, the Rockstar Energy Open represented a return to their roots-a core skateboarding contest without too much at stake.\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1415, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1161, \"end\": 1166, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rod_Carew\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.897822566704426e-20, \"text\": \"Carew\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rod_Carew\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rod_Carew\"}, {\"begin\": 1303, \"end\": 1318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rockstar_(drink)\", \"score\": 0.9999999999922693, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rockstar Energy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rockstar_(drink)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rockstar_(drink)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the dozens\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1181}, {\"ngram\": \"other invited skateboarders\", \"from\": 1185, \"to\": 1212}, {\"ngram\": \"the two-year process\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1244}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1297}, {\"ngram\": \"a return\", \"from\": 1336, \"to\": 1344}, {\"ngram\": \"their roots\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1359}, {\"ngram\": \"a core skateboarding contest\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1388}, {\"ngram\": \"stake\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1414}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A lot of us just feel like a weight has been taken off our shoulders,\\\" said two-time Olympic gold medalist Keegan Palmer, who competes for Australia.\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1567, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1525, \"end\": 1538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keegan_Palmer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keegan Palmer\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keegan_Palmer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keegan_Palmer\"}, {\"begin\": 1557, \"end\": 1566, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.9381602020966949, \"rank\": 0.06589053031694028, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A lot\", \"from\": 1418, \"to\": 1423}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1429}, {\"ngram\": \"a weight\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 1453}, {\"ngram\": \"our shoulders\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1486}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a lot more relaxed.\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1594, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If I did not make it to finals [here], I'd still go to sleep fine.\", \"from\": 1595, \"to\": 1661, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 1619, \"to\": 1625}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But if I did not make it to the Olympics, I am gonna be crying at home,\\\" Palmer added, laughing.\", \"from\": 1662, \"to\": 1758, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1690, \"to\": 1702}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 1728, \"to\": 1732}, {\"ngram\": \"Palmer\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1741}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is like what I was kind of introduced to as contest skating, was contests like this, so it's nostalgic for me, like going back to the old days,\\\" Paris 2024 silver medalist Tom Schaar said.\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1954, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1911, \"end\": 1921, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8164551334260353e-18, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1938, \"end\": 1948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Schaar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Schaar\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Schaar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Schaar\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"contest skating\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1825}, {\"ngram\": \"contests\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1839}, {\"ngram\": \"the old days\", \"from\": 1896, \"to\": 1908}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Schaar, who landed the first 1080 in skateboarding in 2012 at the age of 12, established his transition skating prowess at Vans Pool Party and other core contests.\", \"from\": 1956, \"to\": 2119, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2079, \"end\": 2083, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.551183853619511e-31, \"text\": \"Vans\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vans\"}, {\"begin\": 2084, \"end\": 2094, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pool_Party_(The_Office)\", \"score\": 0.9801941717650889, \"rank\": 0.020202020202019867, \"text\": \"Pool Party\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pool_Party_(The_Office)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pool_Party_(The_Office)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Schaar\", \"from\": 1956, \"to\": 1962}, {\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 2018, \"to\": 2025}, {\"ngram\": \"his transition skating prowess\", \"from\": 2045, \"to\": 2075}, {\"ngram\": \"other core contests\", \"from\": 2099, \"to\": 2118}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everyone that used to do the old contests is here skating too, so it's more relaxed, no pressure, just having fun,\\\" Schaar added.\", \"from\": 2121, \"to\": 2251, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everyone\", \"from\": 2122, \"to\": 2130}, {\"ngram\": \"the old contests\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2163}, {\"ngram\": \"no pressure\", \"from\": 2207, \"to\": 2218}, {\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 2232, \"to\": 2235}, {\"ngram\": \"Schaar\", \"from\": 2238, \"to\": 2244}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The men's park final at the Paris Olympics was the highest level of transition skating the sport has seen.\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2359, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 2277, \"to\": 2295}, {\"ngram\": \"the highest level\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2317}, {\"ngram\": \"transition\", \"from\": 2321, \"to\": 2331}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 2340, \"to\": 2349}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Medalists Palmer, Schaar and Brazil's Augusto Akio put down technical and highly difficult runs.\", \"from\": 2360, \"to\": 2456, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2370, \"end\": 2376, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carson_Palmer\", \"score\": 0.9960999663528227, \"rank\": 0.003915303220582017, \"text\": \"Palmer\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carson_Palmer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carson_Palmer\"}, {\"begin\": 2389, \"end\": 2395, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9692246762734126, \"rank\": 0.02619116747136025, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Schaar\", \"from\": 2378, \"to\": 2384}, {\"ngram\": \"technical and highly difficult runs\", \"from\": 2420, \"to\": 2455}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Schaar's silver-medal run included a heelflip Indy, an alley oop 540 and a kickflip Indy to fakie-so good it elicited fist pumps from Tony Hawk, who was sitting in the crowd and whose Birdhouse Skateboards team Schaar rides for.\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2685, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2641, \"end\": 2662, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Birdhouse_Skateboards\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Birdhouse Skateboards\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Birdhouse_Skateboards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Birdhouse_Skateboards\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Schaar's silver-medal run\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2482}, {\"ngram\": \"a heelflip Indy\", \"from\": 2492, \"to\": 2507}, {\"ngram\": \"an alley oop\", \"from\": 2509, \"to\": 2521}, {\"ngram\": \"a kickflip Indy\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2545}, {\"ngram\": \"fist pumps\", \"from\": 2575, \"to\": 2585}, {\"ngram\": \"Tony Hawk\", \"from\": 2591, \"to\": 2600}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowd\", \"from\": 2621, \"to\": 2630}, {\"ngram\": \"Schaar\", \"from\": 2668, \"to\": 2674}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Compare the enormous Paris park course with its 18 features to the Rockstar Energy Open, where the bowl was smaller and more straightforward-just a back-to-basics backyard setup.\", \"from\": 2687, \"to\": 2865, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2708, \"end\": 2713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999877218, \"rank\": 1.205714230314294e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2754, \"end\": 2769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rockstar_(drink)\", \"score\": 0.9999999999922693, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rockstar Energy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rockstar_(drink)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rockstar_(drink)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its 18 features\", \"from\": 2731, \"to\": 2746}, {\"ngram\": \"the bowl\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2790}, {\"ngram\": \"basics\", \"from\": 2843, \"to\": 2849}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The men did not wear pads, because this wasn't that kind of contest.\", \"from\": 2866, \"to\": 2934, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The men\", \"from\": 2866, \"to\": 2873}, {\"ngram\": \"pads\", \"from\": 2887, \"to\": 2891}, {\"ngram\": \"that kind\", \"from\": 2913, \"to\": 2922}, {\"ngram\": \"contest\", \"from\": 2926, \"to\": 2933}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a result, the tricks were not as big (though Rockstar Energy Open winner Yuro Nagahara still managed a kickflip Indy transfer off the extension wall and a huge backside 540).\", \"from\": 2935, \"to\": 3112, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2983, \"end\": 2998, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rockstar_(drink)\", \"score\": 0.9999999999922693, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rockstar Energy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rockstar_(drink)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rockstar_(drink)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a result\", \"from\": 2938, \"to\": 2946}, {\"ngram\": \"the tricks\", \"from\": 2948, \"to\": 2958}, {\"ngram\": \"a kickflip Indy\", \"from\": 3039, \"to\": 3054}, {\"ngram\": \"the extension wall\", \"from\": 3068, \"to\": 3086}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge backside\", \"from\": 3091, \"to\": 3106}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As Carew put it, \\\"Here it's much more about style.\\\"\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3165, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3117, \"end\": 3122, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rod_Carew\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.897822566704426e-20, \"text\": \"Carew\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rod_Carew\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rod_Carew\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"style\", \"from\": 3158, \"to\": 3163}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For Minna Stess, who represented the U.S. at the Paris Games, it was \\\"such a breath of fresh air\\\" to skate in a contest and not have to worry about earning enough Olympic qualifying points to be one of the top three Americans in the world rankings.\", \"from\": 3167, \"to\": 3415, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3171, \"end\": 3176, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minna\", \"score\": 0.9999999847750588, \"rank\": 1.522512372165516e-08, \"text\": \"Minna\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minna\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minna\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 3200, \"to\": 3208}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 3212, \"to\": 3227}, {\"ngram\": \"such a breath\", \"from\": 3237, \"to\": 3250}, {\"ngram\": \"fresh air\", \"from\": 3254, \"to\": 3263}, {\"ngram\": \"a contest\", \"from\": 3277, \"to\": 3286}, {\"ngram\": \"enough Olympic qualifying points\", \"from\": 3323, \"to\": 3355}, {\"ngram\": \"the top three Americans\", \"from\": 3369, \"to\": 3392}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 3396, \"to\": 3405}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have never had this much fun at a contest,\\\" Stess said.\", \"from\": 3417, \"to\": 3475, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this much fun\", \"from\": 3435, \"to\": 3448}, {\"ngram\": \"a contest\", \"from\": 3452, \"to\": 3461}, {\"ngram\": \"Stess\", \"from\": 3464, \"to\": 3469}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stess finished just off the podium in fourth at the Rockstar Energy Open, but she still accomplished what she set out to do.\", \"from\": 3477, \"to\": 3601, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3529, \"end\": 3544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rockstar_(drink)\", \"score\": 0.9999999999922693, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rockstar Energy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rockstar_(drink)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rockstar_(drink)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Stess\", \"from\": 3477, \"to\": 3482}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 3501, \"to\": 3511}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am just happy to put down a run because I did not get to put one down in Paris and I was kind of bummed,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3603, \"to\": 3721, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3679, \"end\": 3684, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999877218, \"rank\": 1.205714230314294e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a run\", \"from\": 3632, \"to\": 3637}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My only goal for any contest is just to land a run and that's what I did, so I am like okay, third, fourth-I do not care.\", \"from\": 3722, \"to\": 3844, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My only goal\", \"from\": 3723, \"to\": 3735}, {\"ngram\": \"any contest\", \"from\": 3740, \"to\": 3751}, {\"ngram\": \"a run\", \"from\": 3768, \"to\": 3773}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As long as I put down what I wanted to.\\\"\", \"from\": 3845, \"to\": 3885, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's different from the Olympics because the Olympics is more like you have to really focus on yourself,\\\" two-time U.S. Olympian Bryce Wettstein said about the environment at the Rockstar Energy Open.\", \"from\": 3887, \"to\": 4088, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4008, \"end\": 4016, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999997207851, \"rank\": 2.791603655724014e-10, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 4017, \"end\": 4032, \"title\": \"http://dbped